
1. Add dependencies 
 
  sudo apt-get install julius libjulius-dev libasound2-dev 
 
2. Move the directory qbo-julius-model and all its contents into your root directory 
 
  sudo mv /opt/ros/hydro/stacks/qbo_listen/Dependencies/qbo-julius-model /usr/share/ 
  sudo chmod 777 -R /usr/share/qbo-julius-model 
   
 
3. In order to run qbo_listen node you must first compile the grammar directories (en , es) 
 
Use the terminal command 
 
/opt/ros/electric/stacks/qbo_stack/qbo_listen/config/bin/gen_all_grammar.sh 
 
  Input "y" for all cases. 
 
***  You should also check the OpenQbo wiki for more information on how to use this package effectively  ***  
 
  http://openqbo.org/wiki/doku.php?id=qbo_apps:ros_pack:qbo_listen
 
